- cs.MS (Mathematical Software) is also likely as the paper uses a numerical method widely used in fluid dynamics.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is another possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of the numerical method on different parallel architectures.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper discusses the ease of development of UPC compared to MPI.
- cs.PF (Performance) is also a possible category as the paper evaluates the performance of the UPC code and compares it with MPI.
